('armour_multiplier', 2, 1, 50, 'This specifies the amount of damage that must be done to kill a single unit of Armour.\r\n<br />1 is normal damage (it will die at the same speed as fighters or shields).\r\n<p />This will only effect the life expectancy of a players ships, as armour is the last line of defence for a ship.\r\n<br />Game is balanced for a setting of 2.', 2, 2, 2, 2),
